```r
mtr <- data.frame(year = YEAR)
list <- c()

for (i in YEAR){
    data %>%
      filter((year >= i) & (year <= i + 9)) %>%
      pull(prcp) %>%
      hist(breaks = 400, plot = FALSE) -> hist
    hist$counts %>% sum() -> sum
    x <- hist$mids 
    y <- hist$counts/sum 
    data.frame(x, y) -> dens 
    mod <- drm(data = dens, y ~ log(x), fct = EXD.2())
    d <- mod$parmMat[1]
    e <- mod$parmMat[2]
    k <- 1/e/d
    p <- 1 - pexp(log(1000)*k, d)
    list <- c(list, p)
}
```
